title: Can someone explain why this happened?

embed.description: Imgur: The most awesome images on the Internet.

body:
http://imgur.com/a/Y06NM

Image is self explanatory.... ummmm ok? I check my other support tickets for other things in the past and they still all show... So why is this private...

replies.body:
For security purposes, certain account-specific information that you've provided in some tickets may show as [REDACTED] while viewing them from the support site. This is why you'll see this in certain tickets while not seeing it in others.

If you have any other questions, feel free to shoot them my way. ^.^
I checked my email from when they were sent... the info was not bad....so i feel like the governments is trying to hide stuff kek Riot Style
